title: Donald Trump in music
deleted: * The mystery band MAGA Youth released a 5-song EP on Bandcamp in October 2020 with 5 covers of Reagan-era punk songs with lyrics rewritten to reflect the Trump Era. Songs are "MAGA Youth" (originally "Reagan Youth", by the band of the same name), "Trump's In" (originally "Reagan's In" by LA's Wasted Youth), "Trump's America" (originally "Moral Majority" by Youth Brigade), "Fuck Your Amerikkka" (by 7 Seconds), and "Wake Up America" (by Dayglo Abortions).  All money made goes to the [[Southern Poverty Law Center]].<ref>{{cite web |title=MAGA Youth, by MAGA Youth |url=https://magayouth.bandcamp.com/releases |website=MAGA Youth |accessdate=20 October 2020}}</ref>
